snippet.textDisplay: I'm just so thankful of Yoongi who obviously cheers for Jimin to do that kind of dance. The support and the trust! The way he sees Jimin doing great things. I can't help but cry... I'm sure the other members support as well. I'm just highlighting Yoongi's way of cheering Jimin, please don't get me wrong, as it stamped my Jimin heart. Going back to the dance, this might be very hard for Jimin to do not because he doesn't know how to do it, but because he wants perfection in his every performance. And it's totally fine. It's great to aim doing better in whatever you are passionate about. I just hoped that if he decides to do this, he won't get serious injuries so he can deliver this kind of performance safely. But of course, no pressure. Whatever Jimin wants to do, I support him. I love you so much, Jimin!
snippet.textOriginal: I'm just so thankful of Yoongi who obviously cheers for Jimin to do that kind of dance. The support and the trust! The way he sees Jimin doing great things. I can't help but cry... I'm sure the other members support as well. I'm just highlighting Yoongi's way of cheering Jimin, please don't get me wrong, as it stamped my Jimin heart. Going back to the dance, this might be very hard for Jimin to do not because he doesn't know how to do it, but because he wants perfection in his every performance. And it's totally fine.
